data.description: BUYER FINANCING FELL THROUGH** This gorgeous 3 story luxury townhome offers a high tech commercial security system, gas cooktop, stainless steel appliances, 2 living rooms, and 2 master suites. The first floor living room opens up to the private yard which is complete with a fireplace, and hot tub. Perfect for hosting guests. The second floor Juliet balcony brings in natural lighting and a nice fall breeze through out the kitchen and living room open floor plan. The third bedroom is on the third floor which can be used as a private ensuite, game rooms, or a gym. New HVAC and water heater. This corner lot home is minutes from HEB, market street, and tom thumb. The community features 3 golf courses, 2 swimming pools, and restaurants on the lake with an option to rent a sail boat or cabana. HOA covers the outside including roof, front yard maintenance, water and sprinkler system. $850 annually for Stonebridge. $200 month for Coronado. Come check it out before it’s too late!
